verbose_text: Incubation with HG for 24 h significantly enhanced p21 expression in the MSCs in a concentration dependent manner by 155.3% (P < 0.05) and 268.1% (P < 0.01) in the 15 and 33 mM HG groups, respectively, compared with the control group; however, culture with mannitol at an osmotic pressure equal to that provided by 33 mM HG had no significant pro senescence effects (P> 0.05) on MSCs (XREF_FIG).
